Structural Divergence -> Type of Divergence & Cause of Divergence

Type of Divergence -> Different Focus (focus) | Arg Differences | Different Focus & Arg Differences
Arg Differences -> Added\Omitted Arg (omit) | Different Arg Atribute(s) (attr) | Different Arg Chosen (diffarg)

Cause of Divergence -> Due To Translation Choice (transl) | Due To Annotation Choice (anno) | Inherent to Language Difference (lang)
